Name: Genius! NAZI-GIRL GoePPels-Chan ep2
About the game: This is a slightly different history to the world we know. An anti-war visual novel parody set in 1930s Germany where you play Goeppels-chan, the Minister of Propaganda, and have to keep the Fuhrer happy. This time, the Fuhrer has ordered the production of a propaganda cartoon. Please guide Goeppels-chan, who knows nothing about animation, through her distress and on to a good ending. There's also a Super Good Ending and a Worst Ending available Direction/Writing Nao Minda Illustration Kiichi Voice actors Geli Goeppels/Gumi Kinoshita
